        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2021-03-15T16:33:11Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill extends for two years the election and capital gain deferral periods for qualified opportunity zones. An opportunity zone is an economically-distressed community where private investments, under certain conditions, may be eligible for capital gain tax incentives.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
